Liono maximizes and walks to Lion's point on the beach. I'll stay here and 
think for a few minutes before I go to the meeting Liono thinks. "Hmmmm I 
wish key was here we are breaking our promise that from here on out we are a 
team." I wish she could be my backup for the meeting." Liono at the looks 
Horizon "I almost forgot how beautiful the heavens are." Thinks Key grow up a 
lot since we were at the academy she has become a lady. Even as a maximal and 
predacon we had something special we had love." Liono stands staring at the 
sun set sky "I will not let them destroy this not now not ever." Walks 
towards the meeting zone.
